headline: Synchrony to Participate in the 2026 UBS Financial Services Conference
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF) Chief Financial Officer, Brian J. Wenzel, will participate in a fireside chat at the 2026 UBS Financial Services Conference on Tuesday, February 10, 2026 at 1:50 p.m. (Eastern Time).

headline: The 5 Most Interesting Analyst Questions From Synchrony Financial’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Synchrony Financial’s fourth quarter saw a negative market reaction as revenues came in below Wall Street expectations, remaining flat compared to the prior year. Management attributed this softness to selective consumer spending and elevated payment rates, which offset moderate growth in purchase volume across key platforms.
